    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember that because the Hungarian army was occupied Munkacs there, so wherever they had room, they went there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember that, that we had the last Seder with my grandfather sometime in March.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after Pesach, they put us in the factory in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was-- that was the brick factory, my aunt's factory and my uncle's factory, [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Shyovitz. ?] Still, there, we didn't starve because it was there and they had some food there.",
      "word_count": 17
